      "get": {
        "summary": "Simplified coin name, id, symbol for further querying",
        "description": "This endpoint allows users to see the name, id and symbol of up to 200 coin. Knowing the right id,symbol to pass in to some of the various end point is necessary so as to get the right relevant response",
